node.text:
Did you know that 85% of participants from our #Indonesia Hack said the biggest challenges in their country are climate change and access to education?  Novam is one of our amazing #YOUTHPOWERHACKS participants who is passionate about making positive change in Indonesia. Have a listen to this voice note to learn more about Novam’s concerns around the impact of food on the environment, and why he is taking part in the Youth Power Hacks! 

 #Goal13 @restlessdevelopment @theglobalgoals

Why do they cut down forests for food? Isn’t that because the food produced is used to feed the animals we eat? If we all ate veggies there would be no need to cut down trees. And what do you mean with: if foodwaste was a country? When we know that: Animal agriculture is responsible for at least 87 percent of greenhouse gas emissions, according to a new report. The Climate Healers position paper, by Dr. Sailesh Rao, has been published by the Journal of Ecological Society.
Lawak banget kalo unilever peduli sama climate change
Bonus karyawan yang kerja buat unilever tolong jangan dipending dong. Mana saham turun terus. So so an peduli ini itu lah. Prodak semua dari plastik. GG🔥
